{"tid":1913223,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"南韓取消日本免簽證待遇","createTime":"2020-03-06T15:21:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-07T11:06:42.000Z","uid":168020,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"2ada7f6b292de2a21278361f1d47bebfb39206d2","tid":1913223,"uid":168020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T15:21:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/03/06/232039_9354491b6090d379af6931a1ce1714ba.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F03%2F06%2F232039_9354491b6090d379af6931a1ce1714ba.png&h=3fff9eec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n南韓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=383292\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D383292&d=nExaWN1d7lalHJLKFoHQnPcTfOzAwtSP2zPdisjLlXU%3D&h=4ee4f46e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D383292&h=3f7e66e5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=383292</a>"},{"pid":"b94b8e74f4f2569d12cacff59fe2f4f71e7f8392","tid":1913223,"uid":304769,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T15:23:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />得淡笑<br />\n<br />\n脫離支那是是香港唯一出路，但絕不能直接獨立，必須先經英美託管一段時間再經公投獨立<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1913061\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1913061</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n想消滅支那，我們就要帶領支畜暴動和革命，才有機會從內部瓦解支共（輸出革命+加速主義，缺一不可）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1911527\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1911527</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n唔想香港淪為支那賤畜之境，大家必須肅清中資，整頓&ldquo;港漂&rdquo;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1902243\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1902243</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n（國際戰線）借助日韓爆發武肺推動全球反奶共運動和全球排支運動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1894747\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1894747</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n中資禍港數十年，若不肅清，真香港人恐將不復存在<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1810669\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1810669</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n必須先紅後藍，否則中共恐成最後贏家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1809175\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1809175</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"84183bb5e482578faa058920f7ca79ef7cb25862","tid":1913223,"uid":310914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T15:24:01.000Z","msg":"狗咬狗骨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a3826fc3e9bf2bc8b142beb8110a5a624ac1c1d","tid":1913223,"uid":168020,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"84183bb5e482578faa058920f7ca79ef7cb25862","tid":1913223,"uid":310914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T15:24:01.000Z","msg":"狗咬狗骨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T15:25:48.000Z","msg":"好心南韓直接封中國關仲好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa4461ea7127b204ca8d20c896890343bdeefa77","tid":1913223,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T15:25:51.000Z","msg":"當柒婆連關都唔封<br />\n人地已經玩緊取消免簽報復<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1be98aaf3a45565e897961396a724dba156c27b","tid":1913223,"uid":114946,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T15:27:03.000Z","msg":"疫症大流行時代，互相減少人口流動係好事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1745ad745f1d94a914d8690e5eb574c298a7a500","tid":1913223,"uid":29514,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-0